_json.gridTitle: JAG Grill is Ultimate BBQ Table, Has 8 Individual Grilling Stations
_json.description: Nothing says summer quite like crowding around the barbecue with friends and family, and the Jag Grill looks to bring on a whole new meaning to the idea. Shaped like a giant octagon, the Jag is like a communal grilling station. Not only is there a massive grilling area in the center, but there are also eight different individual grilling stations for all your guests.
